title: Ep. 149 S&A Investor - Jeff Macke Unplugged
itunes:title: Jeff Macke Unplugged
description: Jeff Macke, host of Breakout for Yahoo! Finance, explains why the recent stimulus announcement from the Fed means four more years for President Obama. Macke also tells us why Facebook, Apple, and JC Penney are going much higher.
